      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DRAMATICAL (1) goes very well this trip starting 11 times for four wins and two minors. Below best last time at Horsham (27.37) in a Special conditions G2, finishing a 9 length fifth. Expected to be in the finish. PAW MONET (4) could manage only second at The Meadows last time but turned heads when posting a brilliant 29.97 over 525m at The Meadows the start prior. Top win two back and rates a key player again. ASTON BUGSY (7) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when third beaten 3 lengths (29.65). Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from five starts. Overdue and gets his chance. MOONLIGHT MILLER (5) cannot be left out over a shorter journey.",
